msgstr "Sainigh an gcaithfear slisní a tharraingt deiseal nó tuathal."

#. i18n: ectx: (Loaded from Pie chart) <settings> <setting> (refers to element labelled "Radius")
#: rkward/plugins/plots/piechart.rkh:31
#, kde-format
